reviewText: Just got my copy of Sabrina, the animated series and I love it. half of the episodes on a 3 disc set. Even includes an episode of the 2nd series Sabrina's secret life. The quality is great. The DVD preview and bonus episode was very good and well done. The only thing that needs work is the packaging. the insert was good, but why are all the discs in sleeves? Not sure. But I still give it five stars just because everything else was great. Cant wait till volume 2.

Although I bought this around a year ago, I am just now getting to watch it. The first disc seems to be scratched and many of the episodes will not play correctly. The second disc in the set isn't even recognized as a DVD by my DVD player, so I am not able to watch any of it. This was a complete waste of money!
Great tv show . My daughter and my niece loves it!! I'm glad that I purchased it. Lots of episodes

The only downside I would say about this purchase is that the second volume hasn't been released yet. If you were, like me, trying to watch the entire series in one go; then you're probably going to have to wait!
